{"tid":2448967,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"悼念周梓樂逝世三個月 調酒師及學生被指拒捕 事隔逾年被控","createTime":"2021-03-16T09:58:41.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-16T12:19:58.000Z","uid":240362,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"8fee35e2f3d0279afa067fe939b509678fd7b9a1","tid":2448967,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T09:58:41.000Z","msg":"去年2月8日科大生周梓樂逝世三個月，大批市民於將軍澳出席悼念活動，其間發生警民衝突事件，事件持續至凌晨，警方於行動中施放催淚彈並拘捕逾百人。事隔逾年，當日被捕的一名學生及一名調酒師被控抗拒警員及企圖抗拒警員罪，兩人今午於觀塘法院提堂，申請暫緩答辯。其中調酒師投訴曾被警員誘導作供，要求法庭記錄在案。<br />\n<br />\n兩被告均要求押後答辯，以便索取控方文件及提供法律意見。裁判官准許兩人各以1,000元保釋候訊，其間須遵守多項條件及不得離開香港。案件押後至4月27日答辯。<br />\n<br />\n據報事發當天，大批市民不滿政府在區內設立新型冠狀病毒肺炎指定診所，並悼念科大生周梓樂逝世三個月，在上址聚集，大批防暴警員到場驅散，行動中拘捕過百市民，其中包括多名區議員及記者。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210316/37AKF3J6EVFWHID3CQQPOIL5LE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210316%2F37AKF3J6EVFWHID3CQQPOIL5LE%2F&d=HziU8jWK8j2Oa3ZLfTDirC8TOYGSXSADKPC8%2B0d5FCk%3D&h=6e08bfd1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210316%2F37AKF3J6EVFWHID3CQQPOIL5LE%2F&h=cd938fa7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210316/37AKF3J6EVFWHID3CQQPOIL5LE/</a>"},{"pid":"3a88cb090dd059a726246f64771433736795697d","tid":2448967,"uid":52779,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T09:59:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3541c744cb9645998c30e7a1f465f8e5d39b7b4c","tid":2448967,"uid":126919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T09:59:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" c